QuestData.Title: A Proper Fate
QuestData.Description: Warlord Kalithresh is in charge of the entire Steamvault operation.$B$BI need you to kill him, $n. The naga have left us with no option but violence.$B$BShow him no mercy.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill Warlord Kalithresh and return to Watcher Jhang inside the Steamvault.
QuestData.CompletionText: Is Kalithresh dead? Please tell me he didn't escape.
QuestData.RewardText: I wish it had not come to this, but the naga refused all attempts to negotiate.
